0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:40:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2ee3c561012670518f2751df3e5fab10cdb2e1eb","tid":1678063,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:42:29.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">國際戰線，兩面夾擊！</span></span></strong><br />\n抵抗中國魔掌，需要你課金支持！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>一、遊說戰線：</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">中共一直斥巨資，僱用遊說集團在華盛頓進行統戰，收賣美國政客及團體，左右美國政策和輿論。單是華為2019年第3季的遊說支出，就達到176萬美元。董建華的中美交流基金會，過去五年在美國支出近300萬港元。</span><br />\n<strong>組建香港人的遊說團隊，請支持大專學界及香港眾志眾籌計劃！</strong><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港大專學界國際事務代表團眾籌計劃<br />\nHong Kong IAD Crowdfunding Plan</span></em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fhkiad-crowdfunding%2F&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4corGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=06d38dd9\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/</a><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港眾志國際眾籌計劃 Demosisto International Campaign Crowdfunding Project</span></em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project%2F%3Fshow_desktop%3D1&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4corGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=923b71a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>二、輿論戰線：</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">香港民主運動和抗爭，不斷受到中國造遙抹黑；中國媒體、英文五毛、投共白人，不斷在網上製造不利香港的輿論。為了令香港人不被代表、為了令外界清楚知道香港清晰的民意；</span><br />\n<strong>香港需要一份科學、具公信力的民調來反映真相。請支持：</strong><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: orange;\">【我們香港人】倡導計劃</span></em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209%2F&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4corGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=0d92e5ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/</a>"},{"pid":"21a262e7bb8874e6ca31228603b34ba1a3b223ee","tid":1678063,"uid":335560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:45:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f38ff4790c94d46fa4934f5aa927d6322b4e35b9","tid":1678063,"uid":34589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:55:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cccd25d429bc4127e7286de6572403b319a1a8f","tid":1678063,"uid":56311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T18:07:32.000Z","msg":"pushhhhhhh"},{"pid":"5d1a6add393f21d98066e5e918bbdb29e8c3b7a3","tid":1678063,"uid":217467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T18:26:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1a68690b703d7e161d79773983184a24fda3a4b2","tid":1678063,"uid":175848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T18:38:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d08e3ed5ab85f2151a2d05e7bdd46de8eced5bd8","tid":1678063,"uid":139199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T18:38:52.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa5288c2495c51d2f86fc984421e1eabb117403e","tid":1678063,"uid":73595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":